reviews.text: Cosy, but the wall on your back keep vibrating. The chicken is good. If you like MSG food, it'd be your heaven, especially the soup. But I'm not a fan of MSG.
Of a hidden gem in Shatin area. Reasonable price. Authentic and tasty.  The stir fried beef noodle and curry is exceptionally nice. Recommend.
Revisited again. Tried out red curry and prawn cakes  today as well as Thai noodles.  Excellent quality of food with reasonable price. Difficult to find such authentic Thai taste in Shatin.
Would be a a five star restaurant if it offers more digital payment method

result.name: 農民泰菜

reviews.text: 好味😊👍🏼
喺沙田市中心嚟講算平民價，openrice有不少好評。但試過後就知道非常普通，蝦餅太實，粉多過肉。 海南雞唔滑，油飯唔香有d硬。青咖喱豬頸肉配蒜蓉包係香濃好味，但d汁太稀好似水咁。
食物質素很一般，但價錢卻不太便宜，祗是這裡食肆比較少，所以才有生存空間。最不推介是泰式奶茶，很難喝啊，我只飲了三份之一便放棄
下午茶好抵，二十六元糯米鸡包熱飲，它是泰菜食館，辣味適中好吃，不錯的選擇。😋😋👍👍
做冬蔭功雜菜煲好鹹😫
